self.assertIsNone(get_pending_observation_features(self.experiment_2))
self.batch_trial.mark_running(no_runner_required=True)
sq_obs_feat = ObservationFeatures.from_arm(self.batch_trial.arms_by_name.
    get('status_quo'), trial_index=self.batch_trial.index)
self.assertEqual(get_pending_observation_features(self.experiment_2), {
    'tracking': [self.obs_feat, sq_obs_feat], 'm2': [self.obs_feat,
    sq_obs_feat], 'm1': [self.obs_feat, sq_obs_feat]})
